text: Birchwood Mansions Birchwood Mansions is a block of flats in Fortis Green Road, Muswell Hill, London, and a grade II listed building with Historic England. The building was constructed in 1907 to a design by W.J. and William Collins in the Arts and Crafts style. ==Gallery== File:Birchwood Mansions 08.jpg File:Birchwood Mansions 17.jpg File:Birchwood Mansions 21.jpg File:Birchwood Mansions 18.jpg File:Birchwood Mansions 03.jpg ==See also== *The Gables ==References== ==External links== Category:Grade II listed buildings in the London Borough of Haringey Category:Muswell Hill Category:Arts and Crafts architecture in London Category:Residential buildings in London Category:Grade II listed residential buildings
